snippet.title: Donald Trump Destroys Ted Cruz In The Northeast GOP Primary

localized.description:
Donald Trump cleaned house in the Northeast, all but clinching the Republican nomination. How did he do it? Cenk Uygur, Ana Kasparian, John Iadarola (ThinkTank), and Jimmy Dore, hosts of The Young Turks, break it down. Tell us what you think in the comment section below.

Hosts: Cenk Uygur, Ana Kasparian, John Iadarola, Jimmy Dore

Cast: Cenk Uygur, Ana Kasparian, John Iadarola, Jimmy Dore
